2e18a0929b412ac0e5eba8f21aa195cb132c","tid":1133501,"uid":25831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:31:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b380234dd9bce2dbc58c76188a0486f7e50158b5","tid":1133501,"uid":85284,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:39:58.000Z","msg":"個問題係<br />\n利物浦喺過去呢一個月<br />\n係完完全全轉咗陣法<br />\n無論係球員嘅企位同走位，都有大幅度嘅變化<br />\n仲要喺呢段時間<br />\nFabinho 印象中好似冇打兩場<br />\n如果細心望吓利物浦今季裡面嘅比賽成績<br />\n過去呢個月，得球係偏多，而失球係偏少"},{"pid":"4df77de030b01d219c3226880931702e0bb06200","tid":1133501,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"巴塞學習手下敗將戰術笑死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a414f7af0e925836be3f50c64079dd38d34d0091","tid":1133501,"uid":135910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f725a48c68d541ab4c03ae52ffb2daaae0b7e5bc","tid":1133501,"uid":141664,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:12:36.000Z","msg":"高普用三百場佈局fake巴塞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"勁過Marvel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}